t: "Have you ňĻO Prophetňļ not seen those who had been told, ‚ÄúDo not fight! Rather, establish prayer and pay alms-tax.‚ÄĚ? Then once the order came to fight, a group of them feared those ňĻhostileňļ people as Allah should be feared‚ÄĒor even more. They said, ‚ÄúOur Lord! Why have You ordered us to fight? If only You had delayed ňĻthe order forňļ us for a little while!‚ÄĚ Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúThe enjoyment of this world is so little, whereas the Hereafter is far better for those mindful ňĻof Allahňļ. And none of you will be wronged ňĻeven by the width ofňļ the thread of a date stone"